export const userFormInfo = [
    {
        label: 'Nom',
        info: lastname,
        id: 'lastname',
        type:'text',
        small: false,
        stateInfo: infoState.lastname
    },

    {
        label: 'Prénom',
        info: firstname,
        id: 'firstname',
        type:'text',
        small: false,
        stateInfo: infoState.firstname
    },
    
    {
        label: 'Nom d\'utilisateur',
        info: username,
        type:'text',
        small: 'ex: pseudo, pseudo46, pseudo-46, pseudo_46 (15 car. max).',
        id: 'username',stateInfo: infoState.username},
    {label: 'E-mail', info: email, type:'email', small: false, id: 'email', stateInfo: infoState.email}
]
